(1188, 196, '_blog-page_post-title-6', 'field_624038da04ef2'),
(1189, 162, 'blog-page_post-text', 'As someone who works in the space, I have seen many custom solutions developed from agency to agency over the years to tackle problems like the above. And, in talking to agency owners and SEOs, I can tell you it used to be much harder to do any kind of split-testing before the advent of SEO SaaS split-testing tools, like <a href=\"#\" class=\"blog-page-post__article-list--link\">SplitSignal</a>.\r\n\r\nNow, however, it’s as simple as coming up with a testable idea (your hypothesis), setting up a line of JavaScript on your client’s website (via Google Tag Manager, something similar, or just drop the line directly into the head of the website code), set up a split test in the tool to measure your hypothesis.<br>\r\n\r\nRead more about SEO split-testing: <a class=\"blog-page-post__article-list--link post__category\" href=\"#\">SEO A/B Split Testing 101</a> '),
